示「涉及眾多事宜，不便透露」。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司至今未發布5G產品，與該公司和美國晶片製造商高通惡交不無關係。近年雙方就侵犯知識産權等為由一直在世界各地展開訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏高通在全球的5G晶片開發方面處於優勢，目前而言非英特爾(Intel)可以比肩。在MWC上發布的5G手機，除華為外基本上都採用高通的晶片。由於替代高通的晶片供應商英特爾開發滯後，行業內大多數觀點認為「預計2020年之前Apple都無法推出5G終端產品」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190304/bkn-20190304181906253-0304_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190304%2Fbkn-20190304181906253-0304_00842_001.html&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4PkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=886a18ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190304/bkn-20190304181906253-0304_00842_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T19:51:55.000Z","msg":"唔係幫apple ， 依家俾部5g iPhone 你都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以用既國家已經少，地區仲少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再睇番香港 26ghz/28ghz 依家plan 都未有，3.5ghz又未開始拍賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"地鐵入面4G 都仲可以係Load空氣<br />\n5G 又要搞幾多年先搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2782f6802d89a222b2a433cea2e32a19d795fe49","tid":1046922,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fd0ab09ad808ccbfa2a0a9ba5edd920cd773ace","tid":1046922,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"212871d8e83490c1cac464e8fcb551aabffbd4ad","tid":1046922,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T20:36:55.000Z","msg":"人地做到咁大有佢原因<br />\n笑人之前 自重一下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T22:49:52.000Z","msg":"擔心cook 食緊 SJ 谷種咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"穀！"},{"pid":"afd095ddf7b17699534d175a7a40c4cd99d968ff","tid":1046922,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b7d1d00a06024697be802eb037e8546b651fa9c","ti